The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | The City Diary
                                                                                                               The City Diary
                Police took marmoset theft-accused Raj Saikia and Sujoy Das, alias Bubai, to Alipore zoo on Thursday night to reconstruct the theft of the simians on August 9. The cops interrogated them on how the two cut open the fence and entered the monkeys enclosure. Based on their inputs, the police have decided to question some employees of the zoo.    A man in his 30s died after an unidentified vehicle knocked him down on Central Garden Reach Road on Thursday night. Police said the mishap occurred when Mohammad Sufian was crossing the road around 9.30pm. Residents took him to SSKM Hospital, where he succumbed to his injuries.     Officials of Rajarhat-Gopalpur, Dum Dum and Madhyamgram municipalities met the airport authorities on Friday to discuss issues arising out of the expansion of the airport. The civic officials asked the airport authorities to suspend the project till displaced settlers were rehabilitated and drainage plans implemented. Officials of Rajarhat-Gopalpur Municipality told the airport authorities that they would not be able to provide civic amenities to the airport unless the administration cleared tax dues.    Train movement on the Sealdah-Ranaghat section of Eastern Railways Sealdah division may be delayed between September 7 and 11 because of upgrade in the signal system at Naihati station.     Burglars broke into a house in Salt Lakes BB block, whose residents are away in Bangalore, and took away showpieces, watches and apparel. Cops said three almirahs were ransacked.     Ex-cricketer Sambaran Banerjee will inaugurate a memorial to budding cricketer Rajnish Patel, who died in 2003 because of alleged medical negligence, on Sashi Sekhar Bose Road in south Calcutta on Saturday.                                                                                                                                                                   
